<h1>About Us</h1>
<p>The Ste.Marie 1 Captain and crew are proud to offer you the best of the islands and harbour. Enjoy the skyline, informative fun commentary &amp; take in the sights that our beautiful city and islands have to offer.</p>
<p>We also provide scheduled times of our island drop off &amp; return with purchase of our island tour. Our upper deck is fully open with a canopy that provides protection from the elements if need be, the lower level is enclosed with wall to wall viewing windows. Our most popular area is the bow which is fully open and very close to the water, the lower level also has washroom facilities and a fully licensed bar where you can enjoy some refreshments during your cruise.</p>
